{"title":"扬起风帆","authors":["艾青"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":8,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬起风帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花朵都要求开放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"含着微笑迎阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都爱交朋友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友多了有力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不开放，不交流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活着象死了一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬起开放的风帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驶向友谊的海洋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注，不久前，艾青同志参加中国作家代表团访问了广东。这是他在访问后应南方日报编辑部之约写的诗）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}